We can print our findings in a table, similar to Table 1.5 in the text.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.841409827606931*^9, 3.841409845797139*^9}, {
  3.96332305514114*^9, 
  3.9633230631143513`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b18be256-1f4b-4296-9f7e-\
fabfb8eac725"],

